products.title: Men's Flipside Jac-Shirt
products.description: We flipped the script on this jac-shirt - this time, the cozy plaid lines the inside, while the outside shell is a soft-yet-rugged twill. Washed down to highlight the cool seam details, it has shirt-inspired chest pockets, two-button adjustable cuffs, and jacket-inspired, side-entry hand warmer pockets. Metal alloy buttons. 100% cotton. Imported in Charcoal.

products.title: Mens Casual Premium Slim Fit T-Shirts
products.description: Featuring a cool plaid on the outside and an insanely cozy sherpa on the inside, this is the layering piece that makes us look forward to chilly weekends. Jersey-lined hood and hand warmer pockets. Button front. 100% cotton shell. Imported in Multi.

products.title: Mens Cotton Jacket
products.description: great outerwear jackets for Spring/Autumn/Winter, suitable for many occasions, such as working, hiking, camping, mountain/rock climbing, cycling, traveling or other outdoors. Good gift choice for you or your family member. A warm hearted love to Father, husband or son in this thanksgiving or Christmas Day.

products.title: Men's Top-Shelf Joggers
products.description: Made of soft-draping French terry with a velvety finish and a perfectly weighted hand. Refined details include jersey-trimmed elastic waistband and stretch fabric insets at the leg cuff. Drawcord with antiqued copper grommets. Front slash pockets and two drop-in back pockets. 74% cotton, 17% poly, 9% rayon body. 29.5 inseam. Imported in Walnut.

products.title: Men's Diversion Shirt
products.description: Crisp and cool, this is the shirt to break out when the weather warms, and the occasion calls for something a bit more fun. The nicely textured oxford fabric features tiny, multicolored threads that play across the fabric. Contrast chambray fabric and twill tape trim the inner collar, button placket, inner bottom hem, and side vents. 100% cotton. Imported in Salt.

products.title: Men's Reliant Jeans
products.description: We gave these jeans a hearty stonewash for that worn-a-thousand-times soft feel. And while they have a classic relaxed fit and five-pocket design, we added unique character with railroad stitch trim across the back pockets and selvedge trim at the button closure. Medium rise. Slightly tapered leg. Zip fly. 100% cotton. Imported in Coal or Light Indigo.

products.title: Men's Coastal Khaki Shorts
products.description: Made of the same extraordinarily soft pima cotton as our popular pants, these shorts are lightweight-yet-durable and maintain a crisp look and cool hand. Front slash pockets, rear velcro flap pocket, and low-profile welt cargo pocket offer easy storage. Pull-on styling with an elastic waist. Functional button fly and internal drawcord. 10 inseam. 97% cotton, 3% elastane. Imported in Blue, Khaki or Iron.

products.title: Men's Dappled Palms Shirt
products.description: Evoking palm tree filtered sunlight; this short sleeve print shirt will get you in a vacation mood. The slub poplin texture of the fabric deconstructs the pattern to give it an abstract look. Chambray lining at the inner back yoke. Metal buttons. 100% cotton. Imported in Multi.

products.title: Men's Quad Sneaker
products.description: Quad Sneaker‚ Inspired by the comfort of a favorite sweatshirt, the Puliki Sneaker from OluKai combines soft jersey with suede to offer coziness, durability, and cool textural contrasts. Features a shock-absorbing PU footbed, cushy gel insert, and removable, washable footbed. Wet Grip Rubber outsole provides traction. Drop-In Heel®. Imported in Gray.

products.title: Men's Range Boot
products.description: Made of supple Greenland leather that will only get better with age, this rugged boot deftly balances western and motorcycle styling. Featuring harness and triple-stitch detailing along the vamp — and a cushy, stacked rubber outsole — it’s all style and comfort for these uniquely handsome kicks that need no break-in time. Side zip entry. Imported in Brown.

products.title: Men's Decompress Vest
products.description: From the luxe leather to the delightfully thick, cushy feel, this quilted vest is a sensory delight. Warm and toasty in looks and feel. Standup collar, antiqued metal front zip closure, and zippered side-entry hand warmer pockets. Poly lining. Professional leather clean only. Imported in Tobacco.

products.title: Men's Zip Line Wallet
products.description: Made of supple leather with a just-right vintage finish, this is a definitive wallet upgrade. Featuring all the pockets you need (4 cc slots, cash pocket, and a change pouch with snap closure), it zips around to keep essentials secure. Imported in Brown.

products.title: Well-Traveled Money Case
products.description: No indecisive grousing around with this wallet. Just one quick zip and every pocket and compartment are right there in sight. Handcrafted of naturally tanned and waxed full grain leather that's washed to produce its signature weathered look, it has the look and functionality of a well-traveled pro. Features twelve card holders, an exterior zipper pocket, interior zipper pocket, interior divider for phone, plus two places to slot your checks.

products.title: Men's Duo Belt
products.description: Rugged canvas webbing and supple, full-grain leather come together for this belt that offers utility-cool style. Steel buckle. 1.5 width. Imported in Olive.

products.title: Duality Cuff
products.description: It takes two leather strips skillfully wrapped in waxed cord to create this intriguing cuff. Made by a collective of Fair-Trade artisans, it will add color to your outfit and bring your button-ups down to earth, too. Loop and Zamak metal button closure. Imported in Navy or Olive.

products.title: Ombre Sunglasses

Comes with a travel case and microfiber cleaning cloth. 1-year warranty. One size (lens 53mm, bridge 20mm, temple 145 mm). Imported from Japan in Smoke.
